## Dimension: Relation Coherence

**Definition**: The degree to which edges between nodes are justified by textual evidence and semantically valid.

**Why This Matters**: The argumentation graph structure depends on accurate edges. Spurious or mislabeled edges undermine downstream synthesis and misrepresent expert reasoning.

